cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with Natural Language Processing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields are closely related to NLP. The paper's use of an algorithm suggests it could also belong to cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and its discussion of quantum teleportation could place it in cs.SD (Systems and Control).
